This paper is primarily focused on image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses unsupervised and supervised learning, which are key topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks is also a prominent aspect of the paper, which is a subfield of both machine learning and artificial intelligence. Additionally, the paper discusses the architecture design of autoencoders, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
